<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="576" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,151,573]" pageId="5" pageNumber="576">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,538,404,429]" pageId="5" pageNumber="576">Distribution and bionomics.</emphasis>
Endemic to 
<collectingCountry box="[688,774,404,429]" name="Taiwan" pageId="5" pageNumber="576">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
. This species is distributed in mid-elevation broad-leaved forests of central 
<collectingCountry box="[358,444,439,464]" name="Taiwan" pageId="5" pageNumber="576">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
. The adults were only collected in mid-September in Ci’en (
<typeStatus box="[1158,1208,440,464]" pageId="5" pageNumber="576">type</typeStatus>
locality) where the whole year fundamental survey was conducted by the first author during 
<date box="[996,1172,476,501]" pageId="5" pageNumber="576" value="2012" valueMax="2013">2012 and 2013</date>
. The externally similar species 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Wileman &amp; West" baseAuthorityYear="1929" box="[239,385,512,536]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Hoplodrina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="576" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="implacata">
<emphasis box="[239,385,512,536]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="576">H. implacata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
also occurs in Ci’en but only in August.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
